How They Connect Together


collection.html + collection.js
→ Show all products.
→ Click product → product-details.html?id=....

product-details.html + product.js
→ Show single product.
→ Add to Cart → save in localStorage.

cart.html + cart.js
→ Show cart contents from localStorage.
→ Update/remove items.

checkout.html + checkout.js
→ Show final order summary.
→ Place order → clear cart + confirm.

cart-page.js
→ Runs on every page to update cart badge (cart-count) in navbar.